      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e Handles various reset events, including system resets, PCIe resets, and others.\n\n\nHow is this different from ResetRecommended ?",
      "parentUuid": "1d16e665_5aa96058",
      "revId": "272014c1437960ac5c1516b1586957894df2c31a",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
